          {
            "title": "Example: Create an Express App",
            "id": 121549,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Создай приложение Express, присвой значение <code>3000</code> переменной <code>port</code>, а затем инициализируй сервер с помощью функции <code>listen()</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" express = \" /><text value=\"require\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;express&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" app = express();\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" port = \" /><text value=\"3000\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"app.listen(port, () =&gt; {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"`Server is running on port \" /><text value=\"${port}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"`\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"55\" /><option startIndex=\"55\" endIndex=\"57\" /><option startIndex=\"72\" endIndex=\"76\" /><option startIndex=\"79\" endIndex=\"89\" /><option startIndex=\"90\" endIndex=\"94\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"listen\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Server is running on port 3000\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>express</code>, затем <code>()</code>, а затем <code>3000</code>, <code>app.listen</code>, <code>port</code>.</p></body></html>"
